Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:29.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}走り出せば　なびく髪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:35.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}澄んだ空を　呼んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:42.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}行き先なら　もう決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:49.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}握るたづな　熱くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:53.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}迷いを打ち消して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}心動かすのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:01.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}いつでも君なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:05.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}信じてみたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}出会いがまたひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:13.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}明日をかえてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:21.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}願い溢れる度に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:26.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}ふわり風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}新しいページ　めくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:39.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}誰も知らないのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:44.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}一緒に見つけたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:54.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}君が描く未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:29.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}伴随跑动的步伐 头发随风飘动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:35.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}唤来一片清澈的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:42.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}旅途的终点 早已决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:49.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}手中紧握的缰绳 变得炙热
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:53.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}打消一切的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}触动我心扉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:01.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}总是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:05.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}我开始变得想要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}还有下一次相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:13.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}将明天重新谱写
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:21.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}每当愿望充满心田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:26.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}便会扬起轻盈柔风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}翻过那故事的下一页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:39.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}如果我们谁都未曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:44.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}那就让我们一同去找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:54.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}你所描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到白雪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧比！欧比！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就带你前往与你更加相衬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹肯定也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…海蛇！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你从城堡里带出来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当只剩我们俩时 被刚才那女人的同伙袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说 我被拐走了两次！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 你已经回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
